seed_pair.target: No él no quería dejarme solo.
seed_pair.known: No he didn't want to leave me on my own.
Even if he wanted to he wouldn't be able to.

seed_pair.target: Ella necesitaba correr alrededor del campo.
seed_pair.known: She needed to run around the field.
He didn't need to appear angry.

seed_pair.target: ¿Necesitaba ella hablar con esa mujer que conoces?
seed_pair.known: Did she need to talk to that woman you know?

seed_pair.target: Sí ellos tenían algo importante que discutir.
seed_pair.known: Yes they had something important to discuss.

seed_pair.target: No ella solo quería enviarle un mensaje.
seed_pair.known: No she just wanted to send her a message.

seed_pair.target: Tu amigo dijo que ella no podía alcanzar la cima.
seed_pair.known: Your friend said that she couldn't reach the top.

seed_pair.target: Tu amigo dijo que él podía girar a la izquierda.
seed_pair.known: Your friend said that he could turn left.
Did your friend say anything else?
